&lt;h2 id="7-最终成果与物理验证"&gt;7. 最终成果与物理验证&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="71-压实曲线验证"&gt;7.1 压实曲线验证&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;figure &gt;
&lt;div class="flex justify-center "&gt;
&lt;div class="w-full" &gt;
&lt;img alt="模拟成功复现了压实曲线"
srcset="https://yekq.top/blog/gasphia/p-alpha-porosity-model/crushcurvepng_hu_3d44387f0df98034.webp 320w, https://yekq.top/blog/gasphia/p-alpha-porosity-model/crushcurvepng_hu_9657b2cb0b2d1f4.webp 480w, https://yekq.top/blog/gasphia/p-alpha-porosity-model/crushcurvepng_hu_6f829ae12f808250.webp 760w"
sizes="(max-width: 480px) 100vw, (max-width: 768px) 90vw, (max-width: 1024px) 80vw, 760px"
src="https://yekq.top/blog/gasphia/p-alpha-porosity-model/crushcurvepng_hu_3d44387f0df98034.webp"
width="760"
height="477"
loading="lazy" data-zoomable /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;图中红色虚线为理论压实曲线，散点为 GASPHiA 的模拟输出。随时间推进，压力导致孔隙正确压实；在压力卸载后，孔隙度严格保持不变，未出现非物理的回弹现象。这从底层印证了 P-alpha 模型的不可逆逻辑实现完全准确。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h3 id="72-宏观实验对比"&gt;7.2 宏观实验对比&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;figure &gt;
&lt;div class="flex justify-center "&gt;
&lt;div class="w-full" &gt;
&lt;img alt="对论文中撞击结果的复现和比较"
srcset="https://yekq.top/blog/gasphia/p-alpha-porosity-model/compare_hu_a4445ed4a184fc0b.webp 320w, https://yekq.top/blog/gasphia/p-alpha-porosity-model/compare_hu_dd8f668435520cc3.webp 480w, https://yekq.top/blog/gasphia/p-alpha-porosity-model/compare_hu_2ec18410382a5b51.webp 760w"
